  "description": "Figure-Eight topology with Triangle strands — the narrowest harmonic content through alternating positive/negative coupling. Two simultaneous LFOs: braid depth at 0.22 Hz, filter cutoff at 0.15 Hz. Incommensurate rates (full pattern repeat requires lcm of ~4.5 and 6.7 seconds) continuously refract the spectral content. The Prism character is the incommensurate LFO pair refracting through Figure-Eight geometry.",
